{"tid":2421260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[舊聞] 梁永祥：劏房業主加租上限15%建議屬初稿未最終定案","createTime":"2021-02-24T11:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T11:29:02.000Z","uid":217222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6a8d67afa2584d640728bd5ff7731f7da21a7a7f","tid":2421260,"uid":217222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575082-20210210.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575082-20210210.htm&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8IVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=58f48d9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575082-20210210.htm&h=15e6462c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575082-20210210.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n劏房租務管制研究工作小組主席梁永祥接受專訪表示，相信小組下月底提交的報告，將難以同時取悅業主和租客，但他相信公道自在人心，希望市民明白小組的立場，因為最理想的方案可能要用3年時間才完成，最終可能只受其中一方歡迎，希望大家可以理性態度研究報告帶來的好處。<br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n<br />\n報仇咁報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊無魚蛋食, 大家一齊唔開心就最好喇~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390a8b2fc2cbc6b2d6ea16127008598de601eb2e","tid":2421260,"uid":217222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}